snippet: Louis Oosthuizen shot a six-under-par 66 to beat Scott Jamieson of Scotland by a stroke for the Volvo Champions title in Durban, South Africa.
lead_paragraph: Louis Oosthuizen shot a six-under-par 66 to beat Scott Jamieson of Scotland by a stroke for the Volvo Champions title in Durban, South Africa.
